## 🧱 System Architecture

### High-Level Overview


```

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                         Client Web Browser                          │
│               Tailwind CSS UI + Asynchronous JavaScript              │
└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────┘
│ HTTP Requests (Form Data / Cookies)
▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Flask Application (run.py)                       │
│                                                                     │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│  │                     Middleware Controls                      │  │
│  │   • Flask-Limiter (IP-based Request Throttling)              │  │
│  │   • @login_required (Object Authorization Guards)            │  │
│  │   • Flask-CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Insulation)             │  │
│  └──────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘  │
│                                 │ Protected Routing Passes          │
│                                 ▼                                  │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│  │                   REST Controller Blueprints                 │  │
│  │  /register  /login  /wallet/add  /cart/add  /checkout        │  │
│  └──────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘  │
└─────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────┘
│ Secure Parameter Binding (SQLAlchemy)
▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      Neon Cloud PostgreSQL                          │
│  Tables: users │ products │ cart │ orders │ order_items │ txns     │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

```



### Concurrency & Data Flow


```

Form Submission:
User Clicks Button → JS intercepts event → Button changes to "Processing..."
→ Disables input elements to block duplicate submissions

Database Evaluation (ACID Checkout Route):
Flask matches route → Opens transaction block → Triggers SELECT FOR UPDATE on User row
→ Evaluates Decimal balance → Deducts funds → Flushes Order tables
→ Clears Cart state → Commits transaction permanently to Neon

Server-to-Client UI Response:
Database commit success → Flask updates Session Cookie → Sets Flash Message strings
→ Returns Redirect 302 → Browser draws fresh Jinja2 view

```

